Hortense Béwouda (amụrụ n'abalị iri na itoolu n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1978) bụ onye Cameroon na-agba ọsọ nke bụ ọkachamara na mita 400.
Oge kachasị mma ya bụ 51.04 sekọnd, nke o nwetara na onwa nke isii, na afọ 2004 na Algiers
Ọ na-ejide ihe ndekọ mba ugbu a na 4 x 400 mita relay na 3:27.08 nkeji, ya na ndị otu Mireille Nguimgo, Carole Kaboud Mebam na Delphine Atangana nwetara n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2003 na Paris.
